high_descs: To take the watch in the table
The watch and plate move towards the store room.
Put the ring in the plate.
Take the ring from the dresser.
Walk back to reach the plate on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: The watch and plate are placed on the dresser in the store room.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the fridge
Pick up watch from the fridge
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the plate on your right
Place watch inside the plate and then take it out
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near dresser
anns.task_desc: Place watch inside plate and placing it in dresser

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Take the spoon and put it in the watch.
Take the watch with the spoon and turn around the plate.
Turn around the plate on the right side.
Turn around and go to the dresser.
Put the spoon with the plate on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Watch the spoon with Plate in the Dresser on the table.
